content: बिलं {@--1@} A hole, cavity, burrow; खनन्नाखुबिलं सिंहः… प्राप्नोति नखभंगं हि <ls>Pt. 3. 17</ls>; <ls>R. 12. 5.</ls> {@--2@} A gap, pit, chasm. {@--3@} An aperture, opening, outlet. {@--4@} A cave, hollow. {@--5@} The hollow of a dish. {@--6@} The vagina. --लः {@--1@} <ab>N.</ab> of उच्चैःश्रवस्, the horse of Indra. {@--2@} A sort of cane.
